AI agents often work well in demos but struggle in production when crashes,=
 restarts, and long-running tasks cause them to lose state and execution co=
ntext.
These challenges mirror those encountered during the rise of distributed mi=
croservices: handling failures, preserving state, managing retries, and mai=
ntaining visibility across complex workflows.
