NotebookLM just leveled up. It used to be a smart document reader. Now it a=
cts more like a research partner that actually does work for you.
The big idea here is
agentic AI
, meaning the tool can plan and execute multi-step tasks on its own, withou=
t you prompting every single step. Give it a goal, it figures out the path.
Here is what is new:
Runs code inside your notebook
: each notebook now has a secure cloud computer, so it can write and execut=
e code to crunch data and generate charts on the spot
Finds its own sources
: start with just a loose idea and it crawls the web to build your source l=
ibrary, with your permission
New export formats
: PDF, DOCX, XLSX, PPTX, CSV, JSON, PNG, SVG and more, all downloadable dir=
ectly
Powered by Gemini 3.5 with visible step-by-step reasoning so you can see ho=
w it thinks
In Google's own tests, the upgrade beat the old system in over 65% of compa=
risons. Currently rolling out to Google AI Ultra subscribers first.
