<div style=3D"margin-top:0;">
<p>Most AI coding benchmarks ask one question: does the code work? <b>Front=
ierCode</b>, a new benchmark from Cognition, asks something harder: would a=
 real maintainer actually merge it?</p><p>That shift matters. AI models hav=
