The big idea here is <b>agentic AI</b>, meaning the tool can plan and execu=
te multi-step tasks on its own, without you prompting every single step. Gi=
ve it a goal, it figures out the path.</p><p>Here is what is new:</p><ul><l=
i><b>Runs code inside your notebook</b>: each notebook now has a secure clo=
ud computer, so it can write and execute code to crunch data and generate c=
harts on the spot</li><li><b>Finds its own sources</b>: start with just a l=
oose idea and it crawls the web to build your source library, with your per=
mission</li><li><b>New export formats</b>: PDF, DOCX, XLSX, PPTX, CSV, JSON=
, PNG, SVG and more, all downloadable directly</li><li>Powered by Gemini 3.=
5 with visible step-by-step reasoning so you can see how it thinks</li></ul=
><p>In Google's own tests, the upgrade beat the old system in over 65% of c=
omparisons. Currently rolling out to Google AI Ultra subscribers first.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
